history.content:
Getting into a good discussion section doesn't really matter for 61B as you're free to attend any section.

The policy is the same for CS 70 too. --followup: Fall 2017 didn't even have enrollments for 70 discussion sections. Answer: yes, that's exactly because of the said policy above :)

So you are free to pick whichever of the two you like. Looking at the enrollments, 61B has 214 on the waitlist while 70 has 0. So that should help you choose probably.
